# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:34
translate spanish hwb_s31_679b4465:

    # Amber "Yeah, alright. I understand."
    Amber "Да, хорошо. Я понимаю."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:36
translate spanish hwb_s31_1131e1bc:

    # Amber "Thanks."
    Amber "Спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s31_c6fd1607:

    # "Untangling the cord, I set the phone down and sit on the bed, then sigh into my hands."
    "Desenredando el cable, dejo el teléfono y me siento en la cama, luego suspiro entre mis manos."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s31_f8623dd0:

    # "Hotel sheets are surprisingly soft. A hell of a lot softer than the stiff rags I’ve been sleeping on lately."
    "Las sábanas del hotel son sorprendentemente suaves. Mucho más suaves que los trapos tiesos en los que he dormido últimamente."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s31_31bbd800:

    # "Downtown Palm Springs, a five star hotel. We were lucky they had a vacancy, let alone checked us in this late."
    "Centro de Palm Springs, un hotel de cinco estrellas. Tuvimos suerte de que tuvieran disponibilidad, y más aún de que nos registraran tan tarde."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s31_6b0ad3f0:

    # "Of course, a nugget of gold can go a long way in the art of persuasion."
    "Por supuesto, una pepita de oro puede llegar lejos en el arte de la persuasión."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s31_2b89f5ec:

    # "I would have sprung for a cheap motel, but every place has ‘no-vacancy’ signs lit up, and, well, I guess I just wanted to pamper Marina one last time."
    "Me habría conformado con un motel barato, pero todos los lugares tienen letreros de \"sin disponibilidad\" encendidos, y, bueno, supongo que solo quería mimar a Marina una última vez."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s31_1f2d09e1:

    # "Especially after earlier."
    "Especialmente después de lo de antes."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s31_132d1276:

    # "Especially before what I’m about to do."
    "Especialmente antes de lo que estoy a punto de hacer."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s31_9202053b:

    # "The bathroom door creaks open. Marina walks onto the carpet, her hair still damp and stringy."
    "La puerta del baño se abre con un chirrido. Marina camina sobre la alfombra, con el cabello aún húmedo y pegajoso."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s31_01f54e64:

    # "Noticing me, she stares down, avoiding eye-contact."
    "Al notarme, mira hacia abajo, evitando el contacto visual."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s31_863f6d93:

    # "I do the same, letting the silence overtake the room until one of us is forced to say something."
    "Yo hago lo mismo, dejando que el silencio invada la habitación hasta que una de nosotras se vea obligada a decir algo."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s31_2d97dfe2:

    # Amber "How was the shower?"
    Amber "Ну, как тебе душ?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s31_ca004093:

    # Marina "It was nice. Got hot really fast."
    Marina "Замечательно. И вода такая горячая."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s31_42268571:

    # "The room goes silent again. Neither of us can look at the other, but we’re both stuck, trapped until one of us can get past the awkwardness."
    "La habitación vuelve a quedarse en silencio. Ninguna de las dos puede mirar a la otra, pero ambas estamos atascadas, atrapadas hasta que una pueda superar la incomodidad."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s31_1d14431e:

    # "Marina is the first to look up."
    "Marina es la primera en levantar la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s31_220ebf54:

    # Marina "Will the motorhome be okay?"
    Marina "С трейлером все будет хорошо?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s31_b9f0a44b:

    # Amber "Yeah. They said the engine overheated. Should be able to fix it."
    Amber "Ага. Они сказали, что перегрелся двигатель. Его можно починить."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s31_c25ea201:

    # Marina "That’s good."
    Marina "Это хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s31_41ced6e9:

    # "The first words we’ve said to each other in hours."
    "Las primeras palabras que nos hemos dicho en horas."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s31_8079424e:

    # "Even after I flagged down a car and got someone to call a tow truck for us, we just sat in unbearable silence the entire ride over."
    "Incluso después de que detuve un coche y logré que alguien llamara a una grúa para nosotras, nos sentamos en un silencio insoportable durante todo el trayecto."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s31_6140b257:

    # "But it was the silence that gave me time to reflect. About how wrong I was."
    "Pero fue el silencio el que me dio tiempo para reflexionar. Sobre lo equivocada que estaba."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s31_848b9cc2:

    # "How wrong I have been."
    "Lo equivocada que he estado."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s31_8a7764e2:

    # "And what it is I really need to do."
    "Y lo que realmente necesito hacer."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s31_0cc5cf04:

    # Amber "I’m sorry about yelling at you earlier."
    Amber "Прости за то, что кричала на тебя раньше."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s31_593bfa13:

    # Amber "I was angry."
    Amber "Я была зла."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s31_6f5aefec:

    # "Yeah, at myself."
    "Sí, conmigo misma."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s31_5bf66534:

    # Amber "I shouldn’t have taken that out on you."
    Amber "Я не должна была срываться на тебе."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s31_314060af:

    # Marina "Mmm. I was being annoying. I should have stopped talking when you asked me to."
    Marina "Нууу, я и правда раздражала. Мне надо было прекратить болтать, когда ты попросила."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s31_cca35694:

    # Amber "No!"
    Amber "Нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s31_6495f441:

    # Amber "You’ve never done anything wrong. It was always me."
    Amber "Ты никогда ничего плохого не делала. Это все я."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s31_540f9599:

    # "Always."
    "Siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s31_0e2ad4f1:

    # Marina "Don’t be so dram{cps=15}aaaa{/cps}tic."
    Marina "Не будь такой драм{cps=15}аааа{/cps}тичной."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s31_6ad012f9:

    # "She flails her arm over her forehead and falls dead onto my shoulder."
    "Agita el brazo sobre su frente y cae muerta sobre mi hombro."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s31_2847fba4:

    # Marina "Everyone gets mad sometimes. Don’t beat yourself up over it."
    Marina "Все иногда срываются, не вини себя в этом."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s31_efb0ee58:

    # "I shake my head and pull away."
    "Niego con la cabeza y me aparto."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s31_b7674ab2:

    # Amber "It’s not about getting mad. It’s that I didn’t live up to my end of the bargain. Again."
    Amber "Я не об этом. Я о том, что не выполнила свою часть уговора. Опять."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s31_252ed066:

    # Marina "Amber?"
    Marina "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s31_caae8a57:

    # "I look at the curtains and sigh. We’re not missing anything, just an ugly view of the parking lot."
    "Miro las cortinas y suspiro. No nos estamos perdiendo de nada, solo una vista fea del estacionamiento."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s31_9ccb5e33:

    # Amber "I just got off the phone. I bought a bus ticket home for you. One way."
    Amber "Я только что звонила, и заказала тебе билет на автобус домой. В один конец."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s31_f2f1f5d3:

    # Marina "H-Huh?"
    Marina "Ч-что?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:196
translate spanish hwb_s31_e44fa820:

    # Amber "The cab should be here 10:30 tomorrow morning to take you to the station."
    Amber "Такси будет здесь в 10:30 завтра утром, что бы отвезти тебя на станцию."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s31_da7180a5:

    # "Marina shakes out a stilted laugh. She’s not smiling, though."
    "Marina suelta una risa forzada. Aunque no está sonriendo."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s31_ff7c4d68:

    # Marina "Y-You’re just teasing me again, right?"
    Marina "Т-ты ведь просто издеваешься надо мной, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s31_99979e59:

    # "I ignore her and continue."
    "La ignoro y continúo."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s31_febf9258:

    # Amber "You can call your parents with the phone. I don’t mind paying the extra charge."
    Amber "Ты можешь позвонить родителям. Я заплачу за звонок."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s31_a56276ef:

    # Marina "You’re serious."
    Marina "Ты...ты не шутишь."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s31_5f354648:

    # "Bug-eyed, Marina freezes, the truth slowly setting in."
    "Con los ojos desorbitados, Marina se congela, mientras la verdad se asienta lentamente."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s31_7d216216:

    # Marina "But what about the festival, the treasure?"
    Marina "Но как же фестиваль, как же сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s31_3dc7cdeb:

    # "She snaps back, desperate to find some kind of rope to pull me back in."
    "Reacciona de inmediato, desesperada por encontrar alguna cuerda para jalarme de vuelta."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s31_d786ef51:

    # Amber "You can keep it—all of it. I don’t care."
    Amber "Можешь оставить его целиком себе. Мне все равно."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s31_8ccad921:

    # Amber "I’ll go to the festival, go home, and get a job. I’ll just pay everything off that way."
    Amber "Я пойду на фестиваль, а затем вернусь домой и найду работу. Так я все исправлю."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s31_ddaad5f1:

    # "Right. How it should have been to begin with. When this trip was about Gramps and not me."
    "Claro. Como debería haber sido desde el principio. Cuando este viaje era sobre el Abuelo y no sobre mí."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s31_7f4a12d4:

    # "I don’t care how long it takes. I owe him {i}and{/i} Marina that much."
    "No me importa cuánto tiempo tome. Le debo eso a él {i}y{/i} a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s31_cb16f5e3:

    # "Marina sniffles. The tears are starting to leak out, but she braces herself, trying to remain strong."
    "Marina solloza. Las lágrimas empiezan a escaparse, pero se contiene, intentando mantenerse fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s31_2636bb93:

    # Marina "Then what about us…"
    Marina "Но как же мы…"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s31_3ede049d:

    # Amber "What about it?"
    Amber "А что на счет нас?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s31_8b71b257:

    # "I feel like I just ripped my heart in half. For Marina, it looks like her entire world has been nuked."
    "Siento como si acabara de partirme el corazón en dos. Para Marina, parece que su mundo entero ha sido bombardeado."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s31_39c15d65:

    # "It makes me want to hug her. To hush her and tell her over and over that I didn’t mean it, that she can always count on me. But I can’t."
    "Me dan ganas de abrazarla. De callarla y decirle una y otra vez que no lo dije en serio, que siempre puede contar conmigo. Pero no puedo."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s31_ab15821a:

    # Marina "Why…?"
    Marina "Почему…?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s31_226ed125:

    # Amber "It doesn’t matter."
    Amber "Это не важно."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s31_25a71bbc:

    # Marina "Tell me!"
    Marina "Скажи мне!"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s31_76d65c41:

    # Amber "I said no!"
    Amber "Я сказала нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s31_230a4ca2:

    # Marina "Why not?"
    Marina "Почему нет?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s31_cb9b7f85:

    # Amber "Because you wouldn’t understand."
    Amber "Потому, что ты не поймешь."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s31_2a1c35fb:

    # Amber "Look, you’ll be fine. Just keep your head down and don’t talk to anybo—"
    Amber "У тебя все будет в порядке. Просто опусти голову и не говори ни с ке—"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s31_5b8a781f:

    # Marina "{size=+10}STOP TREATING ME LIKE A FUCKING CHILD!{/size}" with hpunch
    Marina "{size=+10}ХВАТИТ ОТНОСИТЬСЯ КО МНЕ КАК К РЕБЕНКУ!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s31_93836b0c:

    # "Angry tears streak down her face. Through heavy breathing, she recoils, shocked by her own words."
    "Lágrimas de furia corren por su rostro. Entre respiraciones pesadas, retrocede, impactada por sus propias palabras."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s31_4f4a93e6:

    # Marina "I didn’t mean…"
    Marina "Я не хотела…"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s31_3b005637:

    # "She steps closer and strokes my cheek, turning my face to hers as I try to hide my watery eyes."
    "Se acerca y acaricia mi mejilla, girando mi rostro hacia el suyo mientras intento ocultar mis ojos llorosos."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s31_147f7906:

    # Marina "Amber, please… Don’t do this."
    Marina "Эмбер, прошу… Не делай этого."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s31_5f64f266:

    # Marina "I love you."
    Marina "Я люблю тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s31_85c49e3f:

    # "Please stop. Don’t make this harder."
    "Por favor, para. No hagas esto más difícil."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s31_2234a6d3:

    # Marina "How can I understand if you don’t tell me?"
    Marina "Как я смогу понять, если ты не говоришь мне?"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s31_22785914:

    # "She barely manages to speak, the tears now in free fall as she chokes out the words."
    "Apenas logra hablar, las lágrimas ahora caen libremente mientras solloza las palabras."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s31_6a1ec400:

    # Marina "Let me help."
    Marina "Позволь мне помочь."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s31_f05272f9:

    # "I squeeze my hand into a fist, tripping as I back away to the door."
    "Aprieto la mano en un puño, tropezando mientras retrocedo hacia la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s31_94e49496:

    # Amber "I’m sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s31_828df7c1:

    # Marina "Amber…"
    Marina "Эмбер…"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s31_fbf72cd1:

    # "Her knees buckle and she crumples to the ground, bawling as she squeaks out another plea."
    "Sus rodillas se doblan y se desploma al suelo, sollozando mientras suelta otra súplica entre gemidos."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s31_5ad0c074:

    # Marina "Stop…"
    Marina "Стой…"

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s31_94e49496_1:

    # Amber "I’m sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s31_f040624f:

    # "I throw open the door and sprint down the hallway, leaving Marina sobbing as I wipe away tears of my own."
    "Abro la puerta de golpe y corro por el pasillo, dejando a Marina llorando mientras me seco mis propias lágrimas."

# game/script/hwb_s31.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s31_94e49496_2:

    # Amber "I’m sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

